content:
error_code: 0x8004010F
error_description: Outlook data file cannot be accessed
recommended_action: Run PST repair tool (scanpst.exe) and verify Outlook profile settings.

error_code: 0x80070005
error_description: Access denied to banking system module
recommended_action: Ensure the user has the correct Active Directory permissions and retry.

error_code: 0x80090016
error_description: Cryptographic service error in token signing
recommended_action: Reset TPM and restart secure sign-in service.

error_code: ERR_CONNECTION_TIMED_OUT
error_description: Banking dashboard fails to load
recommended_action: Check internal VPN or proxy server configurations.

error_code: 0x8024402F
error_description: Windows Update failure affecting compliance policy
recommended_action: Restart Windows Update services and verify firewall/proxy.

error_code: 0x80073CF9
error_description: Banking mobile app installation failed
recommended_action: Clear Windows Store cache and ensure sufficient space.

error_code: 0xC004C003
error_description: License server rejected activation in secure workstation
recommended_action: Verify activation key or escalate to IT compliance team.

error_code: 0x80072EFE
error_description: Secure tunnel to core banking API terminated
recommended_action: Verify system time and TLS certificate validity.

error_code: 0x0000007B
error_description: Inaccessible boot device on ATM terminal
recommended_action: Check BIOS boot order and run disk repair tools.

error_code: ERR_NAME_NOT_RESOLVED
error_description: Core banking domain cannot be reached
recommended_action: Check DNS settings and corporate firewall policies.

error_code: 0x800705B4
error_description: Update for security scanner timed out
recommended_action: Manually restart scanner service and retry the update.

error_code: 0x800F081F
error_description: Source files for regulatory compliance module missing
recommended_action: Use DISM with corporate image source to reinstall.

error_code: DRIVER_IRQL_NOT_LESS_OR_EQUAL
error_description: Driver crash on smart card reader
recommended_action: Update or rollback driver and test with backup device.

error_code: 0x80200056
error_description: Update interrupted on secure workstation
recommended_action: Ensure user does not reboot system mid-update.

error_code: 0x80070643
error_description: Installation failure for audit tool
recommended_action: Disable antivirus and run installer as administrator.

error_code: ERR_NETWORK_ACCESS_DENIED
error_description: Banking app blocked from accessing network
recommended_action: Check proxy group policy and SSL inspection rules.

error_code: 0x80070035
error_description: Unable to access shared folder with reports
recommended_action: Verify network path

error_code: 0x800B0109
error_description: Untrusted root certificate detected in SSO
recommended_action: Update trusted root store or apply internal certificate patch.

error_code: 0xC000021A
error_description: Secure login service terminated unexpectedly
recommended_action: Reboot into Safe Mode and restore from last known config.

error_code: 0x80004005
error_description: Unspecified failure during database sync
recommended_action: Check SQL service health and retry replication manually.
